cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about single image super-resolution (SISR) using deep learning techniques. The most relevant sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also discusses the use of adversarial learning, which falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of U-Net and progressive growing of neural architecture suggests the involvement of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also deals with image processing and graphics, which are covered by cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia) sub-categories.
